trans-unit.source: Represents a text effect that can be applied to text objects.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje efekt tekstu, który można zastosować do obiektów tekstu.

trans-unit.source: The TextEffect object allows you to add effects, such as animations, to text objects, such as <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>, <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>, and <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> objects.
trans-unit.target: Obiekt TextEffect umożliwia efektów, takich jak animacji, obiekty tekstowe, takich jak <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>, <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>, i <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>obiektów.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>
